sequenceDiagram
  participant Worker as Worker Laptop
  participant LAN as Wi-Fi / LAN Transport
  participant Master as Master Laptop
  participant Gov as multi_ai_governance

  Worker->>LAN: advertise readiness
  Worker->>LAN: discover master
  Worker->>LAN: worker_join_request (bootstrap)
  LAN->>Master: join request packet
  Master->>Gov: evaluate worker join / trust / assignment policy
  Gov-->>Master: allow / warn / block / require_owner_approval
  Master->>LAN: assignment_packet
  LAN->>Worker: assignment_packet
  Worker->>LAN: heartbeat packets
  LAN->>Master: heartbeat packets
  Worker->>LAN: worker_result / completion
  LAN->>Master: completion packet
  Master->>Gov: acknowledge and review result
  Gov-->>Master: final decision / review state
